trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"></xref> column that hosts <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox"></xref> controls in its cells.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"> </xref> kolonnen som er vert for <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox"> </xref> kontroller i celler.

trans-unit.source: Use DataGridComboBoxColumn to display data where there is a set of items to choose from, such as an enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Bruk DataGridComboBoxColumn til å vise data der det er en liste med elementer å velge mellom, for eksempel en opplisting.

trans-unit.source: DataGridComboBoxColumn allows users to select an item from a drop-down list.
trans-unit.target: DataGridComboBoxColumn tillater at brukere velger et element fra en rullegardinliste.

trans-unit.source: The following illustration shows a DataGridComboBoxColumn.
trans-unit.target: Illustrasjonen nedenfor viser en DataGridComboBoxColumn.

trans-unit.source: ![A DataGridComboBoxColumn](~/add/media/ndp-datagridcombobox.png "A DataGridComboBoxColumn") To populate the drop-down list, first set the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.ItemsSource%2A> property for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> by using one of the following options: - A static resource.
trans-unit.target: ![En DataGridComboBoxColumn](~/add/media/ndp-datagridcombobox.png "en DataGridComboBoxColumn") til å fylle ut rullegardinlisten, første settet av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.ItemsSource%2A>-egenskapen for det <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox>ved hjelp av følgende alternativer:-en statisk ressurs.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.ItemsSource%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [StaticResource Markup Extension](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se [StaticResource Markup filtypen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: - An x:Static code entity.
trans-unit.target: -X: statiske kode entitet.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [x:Static Markup Extension](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se [x: statiske Markup filtypen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: - An inline collection of <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBoxItem> types.
trans-unit.target: – En innebygd samling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBoxItem>typer.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBoxItem>

trans-unit.source: Once the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.ItemsSource%2A> is set, bind the selected item in the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> to the data item for the row that the cell is in.
trans-unit.target: Når det <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.ItemsSource%2A>er angitt, binde det valgte elementet i den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox>til dataelementet for rad cellen er.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.ItemsSource%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can set the binding by using one of the following properties: |Property|Description| |--------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.TextBinding%2A>|Sets the binding path of the text for the currently selected item.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedItemBinding%2A>|Sets the binding path of the object that is currently selected.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValueBinding%2A>|Sets the binding path to the value of the selected item specified by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValuePath%2A> property.| When the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.IsReadOnly%2A> property is set to `true`, users cannot edit the column and they will not be able to see the drop-down list.
trans-unit.target: Du kan angi bindingen ved hjelp av følgende egenskaper: | Egenskapen | Beskrivelse | |--------------|-----------------| | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.TextBinding%2A>| Angir banen bindingen for teksten for det valgte elementet. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedItemBinding%2A>| Angir banen bindingen for objektet som er valgt. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValueBinding%2A>| Angir banen binding med verdien for det valgte elementet som er angitt av egenskapen <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValuePath%2A>. | Når den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.IsReadOnly%2A>er satt til `true`brukere kan ikke redigere kolonnen og de vil ikke kunne se fra rullegardinlisten.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.IsReadOnly%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValuePath%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValueBinding%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedItemBinding%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.TextBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you want to display other types of data, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> provides the following column types: |Column Type|Data Display| |-----------------|------------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn>|Use to display URI data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>|Use to display Boolean data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>|Use to display text.| If you want to use other controls in your <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>, you can create your own column types by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil vise andre typer data, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>gir følgende kolonnetyper: | Kolonnetypen | Vis data | |-----------------|------------------| | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn>| Bruk til å vise URI data. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>| Bruk til å vise boolsk data. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>| Bruk til å vise tekst. | Hvis du vil bruke andre kontroller i din <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>kan du opprette dine egne kolonnetyper ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>

trans-unit.source: The selected value is determined by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValuePath%2A> property of the selected item.
trans-unit.target: Den valgte verdien fastsettes av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValuePath%2A>-egenskapen for det valgte elementet.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValuePath%2A>

trans-unit.source: The selected value path is a property on the selected item object.
trans-unit.target: Den valgte verdi banen er en egenskap for det valgte element-objektet.

trans-unit.source: Setting this property is equivalent to setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector.SelectedValue%2A> property of <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox>.
trans-unit.target: Angi denne egenskapen er tilsvarer angivelse av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector.SelectedValue%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector.SelectedValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: The binding for the selected value.
trans-unit.target: Bindingen for den valgte verdien.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the path that is used to get the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector.SelectedValue*> from the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector.SelectedItem*>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir banen som brukes til å hente den <> </> *> fra den <> </> *>.

trans-unit.source: The SelectedValuePath property allows you to display a value of the selected item object by setting the path to that property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen SelectedValuePath lar deg vise en verdi for det valgte element-objektet ved å angi banen til egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: This is equivalent to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector.SelectedValuePath%2A> property on <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector>.
trans-unit.target: Dette tilsvarer <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector.SelectedValuePath%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector.SelectedValuePath%2A>

trans-unit.source: The path to get the selected value.
trans-unit.target: Banen til å hente den valgte verdien.

trans-unit.source: The registered default is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Registrerte standarden er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: For information about what can influence the value, see <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om hva kan påvirke verdien, kan du se <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn.SelectedValuePath*> dependency property.

trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the binding for the text in the text box portion of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bindingen for teksten i tekstboksen i den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Setting the TextBinding property is equivalent to setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox.Text%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> control.
trans-unit.target: Angi egenskapen TextBinding tilsvarer innstillingen av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox.Text%2A>-egenskapen til det <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox.Text%2A>
